<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1433,1676]" pageId="1">
Described for the single male from West Sumatra. Recently collected near to the 
<typeStatus box="[1053,1101,1434,1460]" pageId="1">type</typeStatus>
locality: Harau Valley, cca 
<quantity metricMagnitude="4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="1" unit="km" value="20.0">20 km</quantity>
N of Payakumbuh, 
<quantity box="[415,489,1469,1496]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.0" pageId="1" unit="m" value="600.0">600 m</quantity>
, 
<date box="[501,630,1469,1495]" pageId="1" value="2006-04" valueMax="2006-06-31" valueMin="2006-04-00">iv.–vi.2006</date>
, S. Jákl leg. (
<specimenCount box="[783,897,1469,1496]" pageId="1" type="female">3 females</specimenCount>
). A further specimen was collected also in West 
<collectingCountry box="[151,258,1505,1531]" name="Malaysia" pageId="1">Malaysia</collectingCountry>
: 
<collectingRegion box="[269,336,1505,1531]" country="Malaysia" name="Perak" pageId="1">Perak</collectingRegion>
, 
<quantity box="[347,419,1505,1532]" metricMagnitude="4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.5" pageId="1" unit="km" value="25.0">25 km</quantity>
NE of Ipoh, Banjaran Titi Wangsa, Korbu Mt., 
<quantity box="[958,1046,1505,1532]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.2" pageId="1" unit="m" value="1200.0">1200 m</quantity>
, 
<date box="[1058,1223,1505,1531]" pageId="1" value="1999-01-27" valueMax="1999-02-02" valueMin="1999-01-27">27.i.–2.ii.1999</date>
, P. Pacholátko leg. (
<specimenCount box="[162,241,1541,1568]" pageId="1" type="male">1 male</specimenCount>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="1" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1433,1676]" pageId="1">
Only a weak sexual dichromatism was observed: all 
<specimenCount box="[790,899,1577,1603]" pageId="1" type="female">3 females</specimenCount>
from Harau Waley possess black elytral pattern with weak violet lustre while the elytral pattern of the male is bright violet.
</paragraph>
